#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_concavepolygonshape.rst:21
msgid ""
"Note: when used for collision, ``ConcavePolygonShape`` is intended to "
"work with static :ref:`PhysicsBody <class_PhysicsBody>` nodes like "
":ref:`StaticBody <class_StaticBody>` and will not work with "
":ref:`KinematicBody <class_KinematicBody>` or :ref:`RigidBody "
"<class_RigidBody>` with a mode other than Static."
